72
00:04:13,531 --> 00:04:15,131
(is activating a cheat code for gold.)

73
00:04:15,411 --> 00:04:16,211
(But if you've...)

74
00:04:16,251 --> 00:04:18,811
Mom, keep it down.
I need to memorize my lesson.

75
00:04:20,412 --> 00:04:21,412
Sorry.

76
00:04:21,412 --> 00:04:22,211
Go ahead.

77
00:04:40,932 --> 00:04:41,732
Ms. Liang,

78
00:04:42,172 --> 00:04:43,092
what's up?

79
00:04:43,691 --> 00:04:44,492
A windfall?

80
00:04:44,492 --> 00:04:45,652
What windfall?

81
00:04:46,251 --> 00:04:46,811
Windfall...

82
00:04:48,412 --> 00:04:50,251
Not starving counts as a win.

83
00:04:51,811 --> 00:04:54,691
Let me see. What's all this?

84
00:04:56,532 --> 00:04:57,811
So much money?

85
00:04:59,211 --> 00:05:01,451
Don't stand there blocking my light.

86
00:05:01,571 --> 00:05:02,532
Move aside.

87
00:05:04,532 --> 00:05:05,852
I should've gone on store visits.

88
00:05:05,852 --> 00:05:07,092
Wouldn't have to be a nuisance.

89
00:05:08,932 --> 00:05:09,852
Humph.

90
00:05:12,131 --> 00:05:13,371
