91
00:05:14,492 --> 00:05:15,691
Okay. Thanks.

92
00:05:20,412 --> 00:05:21,131
Right.

93
00:05:22,251 --> 00:05:24,652
Mr. Zhou's dad's in the hospital.
He asked for a pay advance.

94
00:05:24,652 --> 00:05:25,492
