124
00:07:19,492 --> 00:07:20,172
I'll go see then.

125
00:07:21,732 --> 00:07:22,652
I'm heading out.

126
00:07:26,052 --> 00:07:28,211
Didn't she resign? How come she's back?

127
00:07:38,172 --> 00:07:38,732
Zhao Mei.

128
00:07:42,732 --> 00:07:43,492
Welcome back.

129
00:07:44,972 --> 00:07:46,492
Why did you bring her back too?

130
00:07:47,972 --> 00:07:50,412
If I'm back,
of course she's coming back too.

131
00:07:51,172 --> 00:07:52,292
You better be careful.

132
00:07:52,292 --> 00:07:54,412
That girl looks like trouble.

133
00:08:10,852 --> 00:08:11,816
They're taking photos.

134
00:08:16,131 --> 00:08:17,891
Taking photos? Come on, take one.

135
00:08:18,972 --> 00:08:20,691
You won. Don't be afraid.

136
00:08:21,691 --> 00:08:22,191
Cui,

137
00:08:23,292 --> 00:08:24,412
