138
00:08:24,771 --> 00:08:25,371
Smile.

139
00:08:25,852 --> 00:08:27,172
Include the company logo.

140
00:08:30,972 --> 00:08:32,132
Ms. Qi.

141
00:08:32,772 --> 00:08:33,811
Zhao Mei, you're back.

142
00:08:34,052 --> 00:08:36,252
Let me introduce you.
This is Zeng Zixuan.

143
00:08:36,252 --> 00:08:38,331
And this is Ms. Qi, our HR VP.

144
00:08:38,532 --> 00:08:39,211
Hello, Ms. Qi.

145
00:08:40,211 --> 00:08:41,451
Are you taking photos?

146
00:08:41,971 --> 00:08:42,851
Would you like one?

147
00:08:42,851 --> 00:08:43,412
Sure.

148
00:08:43,971 --> 00:08:44,851
I'll take it for you.

149
00:08:46,611 --> 00:08:47,111
Ms. Qi.

150
00:08:47,932 --> 00:08:48,432
Come on.

151
00:08:48,532 --> 00:08:49,032
I'll do it.

152
00:08:52,932 --> 00:08:54,292
(Retail, F&B, and Nightclub Sales)
I can recommend it to you later.

153
00:08:54,292 --> 00:08:55,292
That'd be great.

154
00:08:57,731 --> 00:08:58,231
Zhao Mei,

155
00:08:58,851 --> 00:09:00,012
